I think I'm stupid.. -.-" I think those "sirens" where the garbage trucks.. -.-" Wow.. how stupid can I get.. :D Well I don't feel like typing anymore since I typed like that WHOLE thing up there and then I have to go back and bold;underline;italicize those words.. :( Ok.. Well Byeee!! <3

'Kay.

Well from now on, all my posts (and some past-posts), will be friends-only. >_____>

I don't like little nosy brats looking at my LiveJournal. >.<

Have you guys ever had someone in your life for a moment, and when they left, you feel a wierd feeling? Like, a quick feeling of emptiness, or a sharp pain. That when they left, you think to yourself,

"Maybe I should've spent more time with them."

You're so happy when you're with them, and you're so used to it, that when they left, you didn't think that that time would ever come. And only thing you can say to yourself is..

"Gawd. I'm such an idiot."
